    "cta_chart_9J7QnF": {
      "type": "cta-chart",
      "blocks": {
        "row_PwhCtU": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Patented Arched Legs",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Unlike traditional rebounders, JumpSport’s patented arched legs provide unmatched stability and safety, preventing tipping and ensuring a secure workout experience. They also allow multiple trampolines to be stacked easily.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_HttYqJ": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Adjustable Tension EnduroLast™ Elastic Cords",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Customize your workout intensity with JumpSport’s adjustable tension settings, allowing you to tailor the bounce to your fitness level and preferences. JumpSport EnduroLast™ Elastic Cords stretch 2x their resting length and have been rigorously tested and approved for millions of bounces.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_FpPx4z": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Edge-to-Edge Workouts",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Extended lay-flat mats allow you to use the whole surface of your rebounder, making prone exercises more comfortable and giving you extra space for more diverse maneuvers.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_jcaeep": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Most Innovative Workouts",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>JumpSport offers the widest variety of programming, from high-intensity interval training (HIIT) to gentle, low-impact routines, catering to all fitness levels and goals. JumpSport Fitness TV is included with every purchase and exposes you to over 250 different ways of using your fitness trampoline. <a href=\"https:\/\/video.jumpsport.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Try JumpSport Fitness TV<\/span><\/a><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_KFdGFU": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Instructor Education Courses",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Benefit from the best trampoline instructor education courses available, ensuring you get the most effective and safe workout guidance. Get started today with our online courses or contact us for in-person instruction for your team. <a href=\"http:\/\/training.jumpsport.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Enroll Online Today<\/span><\/a><\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "row_PwhCtU",
        "row_HttYqJ",
        "row_FpPx4z",
        "row_jcaeep",
        "row_KFdGFU"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "top_arch": false,
        "bottom_arch": false,
        "background": "tan",
