        "padding_bottom": "xl",
        "padding_top-mobile": "30",
        "padding_bottom-mobile": "30",
        "position": "right",
        "heading_level": "h2",
        "heading_level_display": "heading--three",
        "title": "Why Is JumpSport The Best Trampoline or Rebounder?",
        "copy": "<p>A rebounder, commonly known as a mini-trampoline, is a versatile piece of fitness equipment originally designed for low-impact cardiovascular workouts. But what sets JumpSport apart from the rest?<\/p>",
        "btn_url": "",
        "btn_copy": "TEST BUTTON",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/700.jpg",
        "chart_title": "",
        "chart_heading_level": "h3"
      }
    },
    "cta_chart_6tidjW": {
      "type": "cta-chart",
      "blocks": {
        "row_JdRXYi": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Durability and Quality",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Built with high-quality materials and superior craftsmanship, JumpSport trampolines are designed to last, providing you with a reliable fitness tool for years to come.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_KgdGt4": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Patented Safety Features",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>With features like patented arched legs, extended and enhanced mats, and the smoothest bouncing adjustable tension elastic cords, JumpSport prioritizes your safety, reducing the risk of injury during workouts.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_bYfTYj": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Premium Elastic",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Years of testing went into our selection of elastic cords. Our EnduroLast Elastic Cords stretch longer, last longer, and provide a more forgiving bounce than any other bungee trampoline.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_p6VRem": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Unmatched Warranty",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>We stand by our products so you don’t have to worry. From a lifetime warranty on the frame to 4 years for our 4-knot EnduroLast cords, you can be confident that your JumpSport will continue to perform.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "row_JdRXYi",
        "row_KgdGt4",
        "row_bYfTYj",
        "row_p6VRem"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "top_arch": false,
        "bottom_arch": false,
        "background": "white",
        "padding_top": "xl",
        "padding_bottom": "xl",
        "padding_top-mobile": "30",
        "padding_bottom-mobile": "30",
        "position": "left",
        "heading_level": "h2",
        "heading_level_display": "heading--three",
        "title": "Why Does JumpSport Cost More Than Other Rebounders On Amazon?",
        "copy": "<p>Investing in a JumpSport Fitness Trampoline means investing in quality, durability, and a superior workout experience. Here’s why it’s worth the extra cost:<\/p>",
        "btn_url": "",
        "btn_copy": "TEST button",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/700_1.jpg",
        "chart_title": "",
        "chart_heading_level": "h3"
      }
    },
    "cta_chart_pXtxjD": {
      "type": "cta-chart",
      "blocks": {
        "row_6APCCr": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Gentle Bounce",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Bungee cords provide a deeper, more absorbing bounce, which is much easier on the joints compared to the harder impact of metal springs.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_qiewBV": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Virtually Silent",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Bungee cords are significantly quieter than steel springs, making them perfect for home use without disturbing others.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_eJNJaD": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Enhanced Comfort",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>The smoother bounce of bungee rebounders slows your body down more gradually, making it more comfortable to bounce and decreasing your recovery time between workouts.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_LDwDBB": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Highly Durable",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Bungee cords tend to last longer and require less maintenance than steel springs, providing a more reliable and long-lasting workout experience.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "row_6APCCr",
        "row_qiewBV",
        "row_eJNJaD",
        "row_LDwDBB"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "top_arch": false,
        "bottom_arch": false,
        "background": "tan",
        "padding_top": "xl",
        "padding_bottom": "xl",
        "padding_top-mobile": "30",
        "padding_bottom-mobile": "30",
        "position": "right",
        "heading_level": "h2",
        "heading_level_display": "heading--three",
        "title": "Why Are Bungee Rebounders Better Than Spring Rebounders?",
        "copy": "<p>Steel springs can be noisy and offer a harsher bounce. JumpSport’s EnduroLast Elastic Cords offer several advantages over traditional steel spring rebounders:<\/p>",
        "btn_url": "",
        "btn_copy": "TEST button",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/sxs-about-2.jpg",
        "chart_title": "",
        "chart_heading_level": "h3"
      }
    },
    "cta_chart_7BKGWB": {
      "type": "cta-chart",
      "blocks": {
        "row_dYVaFD": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Increased Stability",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>The arched design offers greater stability, reducing the risk of tipping over during vigorous workouts. This makes it safer, especially for high-intensity exercise.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_BFcMXc": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Easier Mounting and Dismounting",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>Wider legs reduce the risk of the trampoline tipping when getting on or off of the trampoline. Straight leg trampolines may flip up if the frame is stepped on.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_4Btwa6": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Efficient Stacking",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>JumpSport’s unique leg design allows for multiple trampolines to stack easily for efficient storage. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "row_xQdYYC": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "More Versatile Workouts",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "copy": "<p>You can use the stable frame for push-ups, dips, planks, and more. The trampoline also stands up on edge easily, providing you with a portable barre or stability device when doing balance exercises.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "row_dYVaFD",
        "row_BFcMXc",
